  "subject": "Fix failing search-data-service job",
  "commit_message": "Fix failing search-data-service job\n\nPreviously changed the sds to use a new jjb template for the daily docker\nbuild job.  However, that job assumed that we used a different version of\nthe maven-docker-plugin.  Reverting the change, since the old job worked\nfine.\n\nIssueID: AAI-458\nChange-Id: Id8a94922660f9bd21140f4824dc5610289d85b9f\nSigned-off-by: sblimkie <steven.blimkie@amdocs.com>\n",
